10^{n+1} \equiv (1+9)^{n+1} \equiv 1+9\binom{n+1}{1}+9^2\sum_{i=2}^{n+1}{9^{i-2}\binom{n+1}{i}} \equiv 1+9(n+1)\pmod{81}
